io.jeo.util

Class Rect

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.jeo.util.Rect

  • public class Rect
extends Object
    Rectangle class.

    Rectangle coordinates use an "image" coordinate system in which the top left corner is considered (0,0) and the bottom right corner considered (width, height).
